description: The barren trees have begun to fall here.  One has nearly broken in two, the upper half now leaning over far enough so that the top of the tree bows low to the ground.  Blasted pieces of bark and wood litter the area under the trees.
One of the trees here has nearly broken in two, the upper half now leaning over far enough so that the top of the tree bows low to the ground.  A family of eagles have made the tree into their home.
title: [Gyldemar Forest, The Barrens]
